{"tid":2057451,"cid":21,"subCid":8,"title":"結他/Amp/Pedal's 新聞, 歷史, 冷知識趣談(6)","createTime":"2020-06-09T11:23:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-10T17:25:19.000Z","uid":4383,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"471355c199d4f8ab0dea28775d190ed7cb767ba8","tid":2057451,"uid":4383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T11:23:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 繼續傾下<br />\n<br />\n(1) <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/397310\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/397310</a><br />\n(2) <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/561738\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/561738</a> <br />\n(3) <a href=\"https://lih.kg/722187\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/722187</a><br />\n(4) <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1093572\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1093572</a><br />\n(5) <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1154879\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1154879</a><br />\n<br />\n小弟成日search唔同既結他野睇<br />\n對vintage guitar亦略知一二<br />\n亦都希望將所有知識同各巴打分享<br />\n絕對唔講樂理<br />\n絕對唔教你點彈<br />\n只講gear<br />\nGuitar/pedal/amp"},{"pid":"6afbba65b0f57d8ef4b3dcee1c3ad33dd35a1202","tid":2057451,"uid":4383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T11:28:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KB0sdeA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKB0sdeA.png&h=a355f45e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有個老友入左支SG Standard 61 <br />\n因為土地問題 應該會長期放係我度先 XD<br />\n好好玩好好聲<br />\n<br />\n加埋上次自己買果支LP SPECIAL <br />\n呢期都係彈Gibson多<br />\n心郁郁想入支 LP STANDARD 50s&rsquo;<br />\n<br />\n呢年嘅Gibson 真係好唔錯👍🏻<br />\n如果可以平啲就好，睇日本個價日本買Gibson好似平好多<br />\n柏斯折完先等如官網公價</blockquote>柏斯成日都標到好高<br />\n我最近都少左玩fender style<br />\n轉左會玩gibson style<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但又掛著single coil tone<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後買左支66 casino<br />\n雖然好似唔關事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q1UAzMS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq1UAzMS.jpg&h=5e303c56&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>正呀，p90加hollow body<br />\n聽師兄講當年嘅epiphone係貴過Gibson<br />\n咁你而家入手返Vintage要幾錢？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />Casino有beatles rolling stones加持<br />\n貴過Gibson 330好多<br />\n買個刻我都思考緊好唔好330就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後決定一步到位唔好比自己後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n65-68年around 4-50000<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />depends on condition"},{"pid":"cb40fdc0a4a638e2b7b82b0ab192a89579005c62","tid":2057451,"uid":4383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T11:31:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6FPtzZC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6FPtzZC.png&h=b5da9d78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n手持John Cruz Masterbuild既巴打要發達了<br />\n<br />\n好彩我都算係有一支<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0a52fefbaeffea38304a56dd2540bebc028ab0c","tid":2057451,"uid":82593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T02:01:43.000Z","msg":"有冇朋友入左LINE 6 POD GO可以講下用後感"},{"pid":"6c38c9ae79220c3491a2cd59948f120cc7b5de8a","tid":2057451,"uid":10320,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T03:12:05.000Z","msg":"好用， 用黎執歌仲易聽過隻yamaha耳mon <b